        <div class="col-xs-9">
          <div class="slogan1 pull-right"><span class="gold-word">"</span>Choisissez bien <span class="gold-word">votre ami</span> car c’est lui qui vous fera <span class="gold-word">gagner</span> de l’argent !<span class="gold-word">"</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-3">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-neutre btn-ambassador">Devenez Ambassadeur</button>
